<paragraph id="354B36B45649FFFCD1B7FB43FE0B61C7" blockId="85.[108,637,1185,1738]" box="[140,444,1185,1209]" pageId="85" pageNumber="85">VOUCHER MATERIAL: None.</paragraph>
